Places to Visit on Your Holiday Tour Packages from Kolkata

Our trip planners have added all the places that will give you beautiful, cherished life memories. 

Europe

Travelling to Europe is like stepping into a fairytale. From the romantic streets of Paris to the lively beaches of Barcelona, from the fairytale castles of Germany to the picturesque canals of Venice, Europe offers an endless array of adventures and experiences. You can savour the delectable cuisine of Italy, indulge in the vibrant nightlife of Amsterdam, marvel at the architectural wonders of Spain, and immerse yourself in the rich history and art of Greece. Whether you prefer big cities' cosmopolitan charm or rural villages' tranquil beauty, Europe caters to every taste and preference. Choose from different international tour packages from Kolkata to Europe and visit this dream destination of many tourists. 

Asia

Asia is a fascinating and diverse continent with a wealth of cultural and natural wonders waiting to be explored. Asia has everything from the serene temples of Japan to the bustling streets of Bangkok, the pristine beaches of Bali, and the towering Himalayan peaks. You can witness the beauty of the cherry blossom season in South Korea, cruise down the Mekong River in Vietnam, or explore the ancient temples of Angkor Wat in Cambodia. Asia offers a unique and unforgettable adventure for travellers. Whether you're seeking relaxation, spirituality, or cultural immersion, Asia has something to offer everyone. At Veena World, get ready to discover the wonders of this incredible continent by choosing your budget-friendly tour from a plethora of affordable holiday packages from Kolkata. 

South Africa

South Africa is a captivating destination that boasts breathtaking natural beauty, incredible cultural heritage and diverse wildlife. From the stunning coastlines of Cape Town to the rugged terrain of Kruger National Park, South Africa offers a wealth of experiences for visitors. Animal lovers can go on a safari to spot the famous "Big Five" or swim with great white sharks in the clear waters off the coast. Wine enthusiasts can savour the world-renowned wines of the Cape Winelands, while history buffs can learn about the country's complex past at sites like Robben Island and the Apartheid Museum. But what truly sets South Africa apart is its people, who are warm, welcoming, and full of life. Whether you're relaxing on a beach, hiking in a national park, or enjoying a braai with locals, you'll feel right at home in this vibrant and dynamic country. 

Australia

Our travel advisors curate packages that have something for everyone, and Australia is a land of vast and awe-inspiring landscapes, unique wildlife, and vibrant cities that offer endless opportunities for adventure and exploration. From the rugged outback and pristine beaches to the vibrant metropolises of Sydney and Melbourne, Australia offers a wealth of experiences for travellers. Animal lovers can cuddle with a koala, snorkel with colourful fish and sea turtles, or spot whales and dolphins along the coast. Adventure seekers can go hiking in the Blue Mountains, bungee jumping in Cairns, or surfing in the world-famous beaches of Bondi and Byron Bay. And let's not forget about the sumptuous food and wine scene, with fresh seafood, succulent meats, and world-renowned wines that rival any in the world. So, if you're looking for a tourist destination that combines natural wonders with urban delights and a relaxed way of life, Australia is the perfect place for you.
